      "content": "thanks for those points. they're a good start, but they're a bit high-level. for a competitive debate, my students need to go deeper to actually win the round. can you expand on those? specifically, can you elaborate on the 'rule of law' argument and how proponents justify stricter enforcement as a matter of legal and moral necessity, rather than just a practical policy? i need them to have that philosophical weight behind it.",
